{"tid":882960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金傭第一部翻成英文既作品唔係射鵰竟然係......","createTime":"2018-10-30T12:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T14:00:26.000Z","uid":28181,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7998631fe920c6e531dd04d8a180bf667dcc4a","tid":882960,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:48:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">基本法</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n//草委查良鏞與查濟民1988年11月拋出一個被認為是北京官方想法的「協調方案」，供《基本法》草委及諮委討論。[1]方案內容建議立法會分三屆發展到半數直選；而第二任及第三位行政長官由800人組成的選委選出，正正是1997年後特區政制發展的安排。查氏方案中關於第三任行政長官任內，進行一次全體選民投票，以決定第四任行政長官是否普選，以及第五屆以後的立法會是否全面直選的提議，則未有寫入《基本法》內。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksf7X5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fksf7X5R.jpg&h=8e3d30bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKcurZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKcurZc.jpg&h=d0deaf89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8c195c3a9899687e8e04f1ac2c7e8ab797230cf","tid":882960,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}